column5: Happy New Year Roy-dont od' on matzah balls and brisket
I have brisket all year long, matzah balls, natzah much.  Chag Sameach!
Happy new year to all celebrating....

I worked for a Jewish family as a kid (usher at a theater they owned) and all I learned was Daiters and Shopsy's on Spadina. The burlesque next door was off limits lol  We never got the day off  happy holidays for those that celebrate.
Im putting Kosher pickles on my hamburg tonight to honor this day. (STRUBS). Happy new year to all.
